### 正常路径

| 用例ID | 用例名称 | 输入 | 期望输出 | 断言条件 |
|--------|---------|------|---------|---------|
| UT-01 | 标准日程-相对时间+下午 | `text="明天下午3点开产品评审会", base_date=datetime(2026,3,26,10,0,tzinfo=+08:00)` | `title="产品评审会", start_time="2026-03-27T15:00:00+08:00", end_time="2026-03-27T16:00:00+08:00", location="", attendees=[]` | `assert result.title == "产品评审会"; assert result.start_time == "2026-03-27T15:00:00+08:00"; assert result.end_time == "2026-03-27T16:00:00+08:00"` |
| UT-02 | 完整日程-地点+参与人 | `text="下周一上午10点和张总会面，地点在A栋302", base_date=datetime(2026,3,26,10,0,tzinfo=+08:00)` | `title="和张总会面", start_time="2026-03-30T10:00:00+08:00", end_time="2026-03-30T11:00:00+08:00", location="A栋302", attendees=["张总"]` | `assert result.location == "A栋302"; assert result.attendees == ["张总"]; assert result.start_time == "2026-03-30T10:00:00+08:00"` |
| UT-03 | 时间范围解析 | `text="这个周五下午2点到4点代码评审", base_date=datetime(2026,3,26,10,0,tzinfo=+08:00)` | `title="代码评审", start_time="2026-03-28T14:00:00+08:00", end_time="2026-03-28T16:00:00+08:00", location="", attendees=[]` | `assert result.start_time == "2026-03-28T14:00:00+08:00"; assert result.end_time == "2026-03-28T16:00:00+08:00"` |

### 边界用例

| 用例ID | 用例名称 | 输入 | 期望输出 | 断言条件 |
|--------|---------|------|---------|---------|
| UT-04 | 仅时间无标题 | `text="明天下午3点", base_date=datetime(2026,3,26,10,0,tzinfo=+08:00)` | `title="未命名事件", start_time="2026-03-27T15:00:00+08:00", end_time="2026-03-27T16:00:00+08:00"` | `assert result.title == "未命名事件"` |
| UT-05 | 跨月相对时间 | `text="下个月1号上午9点项目启动会", base_date=datetime(2026,3,26,10,0,tzinfo=+08:00)` | `start_time="2026-04-01T09:00:00+08:00"` | `assert result.start_time.startswith("2026-04")` |
| UT-06 | 半点时间解析 | `text="今天下午2点半团队周会", base_date=datetime(2026,3,26,10,0,tzinfo=+08:00)` | `start_time="2026-03-26T14:30:00+08:00"` | `assert result.start_time == "2026-03-26T14:30:00+08:00"` |

### 异常路径

| 用例ID | 用例名称 | 输入 | 期望输出 | 断言条件 |
